OL,3,CMahmood to present radical policing
OL,4,Creforms to MPs
OL,6,FShabana Mahmood will set out her plans
OL,7,Ffor a radical overhaul of policing to
OL,8,FMPs on Monday in reforms billed as the
OL,9,Fmost significant in two centuries.
OL,11,FThe Home Secretary is expected to make
OL,12,Fa statement to the Commons on Monday
OL,13,Fafternoon on her proposals, which
OL,14,Finclude slashing the number of police
OL,15,Fforces and creating a new National
OL,16,FPolice Service (NPS) to tackle major
OL,17,Fcrimes.
