OL,6,FMs Mahmood said her plans were
OL,7,Fintended to respond to "an epidemic of
OL,8,Feveryday crime" such as shoplifting or
OL,9,Fphone theft that was going
OL,10,F"unpunished".
OL,12,FOn Sunday, she promised "a new model
OL,13,Fof policing" that could deal with
OL,14,Flocal crime while the NPS would act as
OL,15,Fa "British FBI" tackling cross-
OL,16,Fregional and international crime.
