OL,6,FMany of Ms Mahmood's other proposals
OL,7,Fhave already been announced, including
OL,8,Fa new "licence to practice" for police
OL,9,Fofficers and a reduction in red tape
OL,10,Fintended to get more officers onto the
OL,11,Fstreets.
OL,13,FThere are also measures intended to
OL,14,Fimprove accountability, including
OL,15,Fgiving the Home Secretary the power to
OL,16,Fsack underperforming chief constables
OL,17,Fand tougher enforcement of a new
OL,18,Fnational target for response times in
OL,19,Femergencies.
