OL,6,FOther announcements over the weekend
OL,7,Fincluded a #7 million investment in
OL,8,Ftackling shoplifting, including #5
OL,9,Fmillion for Operational Opal, a
OL,10,Fnational intelligence sharing unit
OL,11,Ftargeting shoplifting gangs.
OL,13,FPolicing minister Sarah Jones said:
OL,14,F"For too long, organised crime gangs
OL,15,Fhave taken advantage of defenceless
OL,16,Fretailers, faced no consequences of
OL,17,Ftheir cruel actions and known that
OL,18,Fpolice forces may not always attend in
OL,19,Ftime to catch them.
