OL,6,F"My message to them is simple ` there
OL,7,Fis nowhere to hide now."
OL,9,FMinisters are planning a recruitment
OL,10,Fdrive for volunteer special
OL,11,Fconstables, whose numbers fell from
OL,12,Fmore than 20,000 in 2012 to just 5,534
OL,13,Flast year.
OL,15,FPolice chiefs will also be told to
OL,16,Fhire more technology specialists to
OL,17,Fhelp tackle rising levels of digital
OL,18,Fcrime as offenders exploit new
OL,19,Ftechnology such as deepfakes and AI.
