OL,4,Creforms to MPs
OL,6,FMs Mahmood said: "Crime has evolved `
OL,7,Fbut police forces haven't. Fraudsters
OL,8,Fand serious organised crime bosses are
OL,9,Foutsmarting them.
OL,11,F"Under my reforms, forces will now
OL,12,Fhire more digital, cyber and forensic
OL,13,Fofficers to put vile criminals behind
OL,14,Fbars."
OL,16,FThe Home Secretary's reform package is
OL,17,Fintended to both improve performance
OL,18,Fand save money, with fewer forces
OL,19,Fexpected to spend less on back-office
OL,20,Ftasks such as administration and
OL,21,Fprocurement.
