OL,6,FBut reaction has been mixed. While
OL,7,Fsenior police officers have generally
OL,8,Fwelcomed the creation of a new
OL,9,Fnational force, the Police Federation
OL,10,Fhas questioned plans to cut the number
OL,11,Fof regional forces, saying fewer
OL,12,Fforces did not "guarantee more or
OL,13,Fbetter policing".
